  title="BBQ It Customer Offers — How to Get the Best Deals"
  description="Learn how customer offers work in BBQ It. How to evaluate offers, when to accept or decline, and tips for maximizing your sell price."
  quickAnswer="Customers offer different prices for your cooked meats. Higher-tier tables attract better offers. Accept high offers quickly and decline low ones — or use Auto Sell to handle it for you."
  faq={[
    { question: 'How do customer offers work?', answer: 'When cooked meat is placed on a table, customers appear and make offers. The offer amount varies — some are above average value, some below. You choose which offers to accept.' },
